This template is used to present a consistently-formatted table for use in articles about music albums.

==Usage==
<pre>
{{Infobox album
|name                 = Album name. If whole parameter is omitted, inherited from page title.
|image                = Album's image. Front cover is preferred. Format is: "File:example.jpg" or "Image:example.jpg"
|image_caption        = Album's image caption. If whole parameter is omitted, the text "Front Cover" is shown.
|image_back           = Back cover. Format is: "File:example.jpg" or "Image:example.jpg"
|image_back_caption   = Back cover caption. If whole parameter is omitted, the text "Back Cover" is shown.
|image_inside         = Inside cover. Format is: "File:example.jpg" or "Image:example.jpg"
|image_inside_caption = Inside cover caption. If whole parameter is omitted, the text "Inside Cover" is shown.
|image_inlay          = Inlay cover. Format is: "File:example.jpg" or "Image:example.jpg"
|image_inlay_caption  = Inlay cover caption. If whole parameter is omitted, the text "Inlay Cover" is shown.
|image_disc           = Disc cover. Format is: "File:example.jpg" or "Image:example.jpg"
|image_disc_caption   = Disc cover caption. If whole parameter is omitted, the text "Disc Cover" is shown.
|artist               = Artist(s)
|producer             = Producer(s)
|label                = Record label (company)
|released             = Date originally published
|genre                = Genre
|media_type           = Audio CD, MP3 etc.
|disc_num             = Number of discs
|tracks               = Number of tracks
|length               = Total length of all tracks. Format is: "1:23:45"
|asin                 = ASIN Number
|asin_raw             = Manually inserted ASIN Info. If used, "asin" parameter will be omitted. It is usefull when entering more ASIN numbers.
|ean                  = EAN Number
|ean_raw              = Manually inserted EAN Info. If used, "ean" parameter will be omitted. It is usefull when entering more EAN numbers.
|oclc                 = OCLC Number
|oclc_raw             = Manually inserted OCLC Info. If used, "oclc" parameter will be omitted. It is usefull when entering more OCLC numbers.
|size                 = Size (Inches and Milimeters)
|weight               = Weight (Pounds and Grams)
}}
</pre>



==Example==
{{Infobox album
|name          = Example album
|image         = 
|image_caption = Example caption
|artist        = Hans Zimmer
|producer      = Hans Zimmer
|label         = Example company
|released      = July 13, 2010
|genre         = Soundtrack
|media_type    = Audio CD, Digital Edition
|disc_num      = 1
|tracks        = 8
|length        = 1:23:45
|asin          = B003GJSUIQ
|ean_raw       = {{EAN|0075678957611|MP3}}{{EAN|3307211679276|Book}}
|oclc          = 463490283
|size          = 23.1 x 15 x 2 cm; <br/>9.1 x 5.9 x 0.8 inches
|weight        = 481 g; 1.06 lbs.
}}<pre>
{{Infobox album
|name          = Example album
|image         = File:Avatar_Soundtrack.jpg
|image_caption = Example caption
|artist        = James Horner
|producer      = James Horner
|label         = Example company
|released      = January 15, 2010
|genre         = Soundtrack
|media_type    = Audio CD, Digital Edition
|disc_num      = 1
|tracks        = 8
|length        = 1:23:45
|asin          = B003GJSUIQ
|ean_raw       = {{EAN|0075678957611|MP3}}{{EAN|3307211679276|Book}}
|oclc          = 463490283
|size          = 23.1 x 15 x 2 cm; <br/>9.1 x 5.9 x 0.8 inches
|weight        = 481 g; 1.06 lbs.
}}
</pre>
