{{Stub}} {{Infobox actor
|image = Claire Geare.jpg |imagesize = 250px |name = Claire Geare |birthname = Claire Geare |born = 2006 |nationality = American |gender = Female |eye = Olive |hair = Blond |height = Short |yearsactive = 2010- |inceptionrole = [[Phillipa Cobb]] }}
'''Claire Geare''' is an American child actress. She plays the role of the small child [[Phillipa Cobb]] in the [[Christopher Nolan]] film [[Inception (2010 film)|Inception]]. She is also the sister of [[Taylor Geare]], who plays the older Phillipa, and [[Johnathan Geare]] who plays the older [[James Cobb]]. [[Category:Actors]] [[Category:Stub]] [[Category:Production]]

{{Stub}} {{Infobox character |image=philippa.jpg |imagesize=275px |name=Phillipa |born= |died= |lives= |gender=Female |status=Alive |eye=Olive |family=*[[Dominick Cobb]] (father) *[[Mallorie Cobb]]&dagger; (mother) *[[James Cobb]] (brother) *[[Miles]] (grandfather) *[[Marie]] (grandmother) |occupation= |loyalties=Dom Cobb |portrayed=*[[Claire Geare]] 3 years *[[Taylor Geare]] 5 years |first=''[[Inception (2010 film)|Inception]]'' |last= }}
'''Phillipa Cobb''' is the young daughter of [[Dominick Cobb]] and [[Mallorie Cobb]]. Phillipa and her brother, James, provide Dom with motivation for accepting [[Saito|Saito's]] proposal of commiting [[Inception (tactic)|Inception]]. She is portrayed by child actress [[Claire Geare]] as a three year old, and [[Taylor Geare]] as a five year old.
[[es:Phillipa Cobb]] [[Category:Characters]] [[Category:Stub]]

[[File:extraction.png|thumb|right|250px|Extracting [[Saito]]'s secrets...]] {{Quote|''...in dream state, your conscious defences are lowered and it makes your thoughts vulnerable to theft. It's called extraction.''|||[[Arthur]]}}
'''Extraction''' is the art of infiltrating the mind of any person to steal their secrets. Extraction works through a process called [[Dream-Sharing]]— manufacturing the [[Dream|world of the dream]] and bringing the subject into that world, which feels completely real as long as they are in it. Those who commit extraction are called [[Extractor|Extractors]].
