'''Somnacin''' is the name of the drug used to initiate [[Dream-Sharing]] and [[Lucid Dreaming]]. The [[Portable Automated Somnacin IntraVenous Device]] is designed to deliver it. The brand name version of it is controlled by an international control council. [[Yusuf]] makes his own version of it, which increases the effect of Somnacin so that dreams are more stable and time within the dream is twenty times normal. It will also compound the effect with every new dream level.
