== RE: Question ==

Hey there Alquen, I've taken a look at your wiki, and I have to say it looks great! Very clean and simple, great for navigation. The problem that you're having has to do with the shrink wrapping on the main page. What you want to do is add this bit of code:

 body.mainpage div.monaco_shrinkwrap {
    left: 50%;
